 * @constructor
 * @param {bigInt/string} x The x coordinate.
 * @param {bigInt/string} y The y coordinate.
 * @param {bigInt/string} z The z coordinate.
 * @param {sjcl.ecc.curve} curve The curve that this point lies on.
